# CSS Backgrounds

Background properties control the appearance behind content.

## Background Color

```css
body {
    background-color: lightblue;
}
```

## Background Image

```css
body {
    background-image: url("background.jpg");
}
```

## No Repeat

```css
body {
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
}
```

## Cover Entire Screen

```css
body {
    background-size: cover;
}
```

## Center Image

```css
body {
    background-position: center;
}
```

## Real-World Example

Hero sections commonly use background images.

## Summary

Background properties create attractive page designs.
